    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped paneer</strong>,<strong> onion petals</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>,<strong> </strong>and cook for 5-6 min until the paneer is golden, turning occasionally for even colouring</p>",
